{"tid":1774061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【英國戰線】大選民調：遊離票極多，大家齊拉票，平權機會增","createTime":"2019-12-08T04:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T00:09:58.000Z","uid":305299,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8858784b578dce7e7b7a3accd2bf74bcd349ba8d","tid":1774061,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"根據 now 嘅報導，英國大選民意調查顯示，有多達90個選區難以預測，有機會再次出現懸峙國會，依個就係爭取BNO全面平權嘅好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要出現懸峙國會，咁就好有機會保守黨要搵自民黨幫手先可以繼續執政，2010年就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦因為係咁，自民黨政綱話嘅全面平權就有機會落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，大家要叫住係英國嘅親戚朋友，依個禮拜四(12/12)，早上7點到晚上10點，記得去投票，而且一定要投自民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=372593&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372593%26home%3D1&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=c44c7e4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372593%26home%3D1&h=61b75c12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=372593&amp;home=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJBX4VW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJBX4VW.png&h=4d820ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YD4KKVY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYD4KKVY.png&h=1377ccb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L8W1M9j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL8W1M9j.png&h=17ef85ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8vaFuk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A